messages.message: I’m not sure if increasing the resources would solve the problem @Heymian.  I would like us to understand why it takes 4+ hours to actually run the cyprus test-suite.  Are these requests that long lived?

Oh I can’t speak for the cypress tests, would need @Eric Han to help chime in on that, but I explained to you why the system test suites take as long as they do, and I thought you mentioned that you’d try increasing resources to alleviate the number of workers that could do work? Maybe I misunderstood.
Yeah, I understand the system, and stress tests issues.  I don't understand the Cyprus tests and why do they take so long.
